  <brief_title>The Effects of Gum Chewing on Bowel Function Recovery Following Cesarean Section</brief_title>
  <acronym>GUM01</acronym>
  <official_title>The Effects of Gum Chewing on Bowel Function Recovery Following Cesarean Section: Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
